00:00:12.269 --> 00:00:15.490
Greetings everyone, thank you for joining
us.

00:00:15.490 --> 00:00:21.130
We're going to give you info about Otto Bayer
Scholarships from Bayer Foundation in Germany.

00:00:21.130 --> 00:00:25.939
Otto Bayer scholarships are open to students
in their advanced study period.

00:00:25.939 --> 00:00:28.349
Disciplines receiving support are:

00:00:28.349 --> 00:00:35.540
Biology, molecular biology, biochemistry,
biotechnology, biological process engineering,

00:00:35.540 --> 00:00:36.540
bioinformatics,

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:43.160
Chemistry, chemical engineering, material
sciences and environmental sciences,

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:45.210
Pharmaceutics and drug discovery,

00:00:45.210 --> 00:00:46.210
Physics,

00:00:46.210 --> 00:00:47.820
Medical sciences.

00:00:47.820 --> 00:00:54.170
Bayer supports study projects, internships,
summer courses, preparatory and supplementary

00:00:54.170 --> 00:01:01.760
study courses, as well as theses and doctoral
studies (the program does not include post-doctoral

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:02.760
scholarships).

00:01:02.760 --> 00:01:08.829
The foundation places great emphasis on internationalism,
and therefore scholarships are granted exclusively

00:01:08.829 --> 00:01:13.850
to students from German-speaking countries
wishing to study abroad and foreign applicants

00:01:13.850 --> 00:01:16.510
who want to study in Germany.

00:01:16.510 --> 00:01:20.290
Applicants should be able to show good to
very good final school marks as well as a

00:01:20.290 --> 00:01:25.229
particularly good intermediate diploma or
an above-average bachelor s exam.

00:01:25.229 --> 00:01:29.840
Furthermore, a broad horizon and a high level
of motivation and personal commitment are

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:35.029
expected of all applicants be it in a social,
political or cultural field.

00:01:35.029 --> 00:01:40.689
The current application period for Otto Bayer
Scholarships is taking place from June 1,

00:01:40.689 --> 00:01:44.460
2014 to July 15, 2014.

00:01:44.460 --> 00:01:49.609
The independent Foundation Board will hold
its selection meeting on September 5, 2014.

00:01:49.609 --> 00:01:58.029
For more information regarding this program,
pleace check www.bayer-foundations.com

00:01:58.029 --> 00:01:59.639
Thank you for watching.

00:01:59.639 --> 00:02:04.090
Please subscribe for more info about scholarships
from all around the world.

00:02:04.090 --> 00:02:05.299
Have a nice day and good bye.

